            "id": "https://huobingnan.github.io/2023/02/10/Java%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/",
            "url": "https://huobingnan.github.io/2023/02/10/Java%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/",
            "title": "Java单例模式",
            "date_published": "2023-02-09T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css\" /><div class=\".article-gallery\"><h2 id=\"0-Preface\"><a href=\"#0-Preface\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0. Preface\"></a>0. Preface</h2><hr>\n<p>“茴香豆的茴有几种写法呢？”</p>\n<p>单例模式是设计模式的一种，在Java中，配合Java语言特性和JVM的机制可以有多种实现方式。就好比在写“茴香豆”的“茴”字，每种实现各有利弊，简言之，单例模式是为了让大对象的创建得以缓存和复用。<strong>复用</strong>是一种最为常见的，也是在Java语言中优化内存的最好方式。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-饿汉式\"><a href=\"#1-饿汉式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 饿汉式\"></a>1. 饿汉式</h2><hr>\n<p>饿汉式是Java中单例模式实现中最简单的一种方式，其实现代码如下所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Hungry</span> {  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">Hungry</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">INSTANCE</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Hungry</span>();  <br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">Hungry</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> { }  <br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> Hungry <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getInstance</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> { <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> INSTANCE; }  <br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>饿汉式单例模式，可以做到实现简单，并发实例获取安全（单例创建发生在类加载阶段，JVM在加载Class时只加载一次，且只有一个线程负责加载）等。但是这种创建方式在类加载阶段就完成了初始化，若单例在之后运行时未被使用，那么就会造成堆内存空间的浪费。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-懒汉式\"><a href=\"#2-懒汉式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 懒汉式\"></a>2. 懒汉式</h2><hr>\n<p>懒汉式克服了饿汉式可能会造成的堆内存浪费问题，它选择在第一次获取单例实例的时候，去创建单例对象。但这也造成了并发获取单例对象时会有线程安全问题，有可能不同的线程获取到不同的单例对象。</p>\n<p>因此需要在第一次单例对象获取时对方法进行加锁。但是，锁加在方法上时，粒度又有点太大，因为只有在第一次获取单例对象时，需要加锁控制，避免出现线程安全问题。</p>\n<p>因此，懒汉式单例比较推荐的方式是双重检查锁模式，代码如下所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LazyV1</span> {  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">volatile</span> LazyV1 INSTANCE;  <br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">LazyV1</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> { }  <br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> LazyV1 <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getInstance</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> {  <br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (INSTANCE == <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>) {  <br>            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">synchronized</span> (LazyV1.class) {  <br>                <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (INSTANCE == <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>) {  <br>                    INSTANCE = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LazyV1</span>();  <br>                }  <br>            }  <br>        }  <br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> INSTANCE;  <br>    }  <br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>除了双重检查锁模式，还有一种基于静态内部类的懒汉式单例创建方法，它是利用了JVM对于类加载的特性，其代码如下所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LazyV2</span> {  <br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">LazyV2</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> {  }<br>  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Holder</span> {  <br>\t\t<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 按照JVM类加载规则（按需加载），静态内部类Holder不会被立即加载</span><br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">LazyV2</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">INSTANCE</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LazyV2</span>();  <br>    }  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 只有在调用getInstance方法时，LazyV2$Holder才会被加载</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> LazyV2 <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getInstance</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> { <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> Holder.INSTANCE; }  <br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这种实现方式会比双重检查锁的实现方式简洁，并且JDK中也多采用这种方式。JDK中较为常见的<em>Math#random</em>方法，就是采用了内部类的方式，创建了一个<em>Random</em>类的单例。从JDK代码设计中可以看到，懒汉式单例是较为推荐的单例创建方式。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RandomNumberGeneratorHolder</span> {  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">Random</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">randomNumberGenerator</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Random</span>();  <br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"3-借助枚举类\"><a href=\"#3-借助枚举类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 借助枚举类\"></a>3. 借助枚举类</h2><hr>\n<p>枚举类是Java编译器对于单例的一种实现，Java代码的枚举类的每个字段，在编译阶段会被处理为一个单例对象，其代码如下所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">enum</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Config</span> {  <br>    INSTANCE;  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> String name;  <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> scale;  <br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js\"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {\n        var options = {\n            selector: '.gallery-item'\n        };\n        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);\n        }</script>",
